title: Limited Time Pricing! Call Today. Last Renovated Unit Available!
posting_body: Welcome Home to Bayview Apartment Homes
This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 910 Sq.
At Bayview Apartment Homes, service and convenience are our specialties.
We are situated between Tacoma and Seattle in Federal Way, and all of Greater King County is within easy reach.
Our controlled-access building is home to studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments for rent, and we offer numerous amenities to ensure our residents' comfort.
Whether you are a single person looking for your first apartment or you are searching for a new place for your family to call home, Bayview is an excellent choice.
We are a pet-friendly complex, so we even welcome your furry family members.
Bayview Apartment Homes welcomes your furry loved ones with some weight and breed restrictions.
Please contact the management office for more information.
